03/episode/427769/summary.html | accessdate = 2009-05-06}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:95%; white-space:nowrap\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%\"|Couple\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Scores\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Dance\n! style=\"width:44%\"|Music\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Result\n|-\n| Evander & Camilla\n| 13 (5, 4, 4)\n| Jive\n| \"[[Reet Petite]]\"\u2014[[Jackie Wilson]]\n| Eliminated\n|-\n| Rachel & Ian\n| 26 (8, 9, 9)\n|Tango\n| \"[[Toxic (song)|Toxic]]\"\u2014[[Britney Spears]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| Kelly & Brendan\n| 21 (6, 7, 8)\n| Jive\n| \"[[Footloose (song)|Footloose]]\"\u2014[[Kenny Loggins]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| John & Nicole\n| 24 (9, 8, 7)\n| Tango\n| \"[[Dance with Me (Debelah Morgan song)|Dance with Me]]\"\u2014[[Debelah Morgan]]\n|Safe\n|-\n| Joey & Erin\n| 22 (7, 7, 8)\n| Jive\n| \"[[I'm Still Standing]]\"\u2014[[Elton John]]\n| Bottom two\n|}\n\n===Week 4===\n;Running order<ref>{{cite web | title = Dancing with the Stars: Episode 104 | publisher = TV.com | url = http://www.tv.com/Dancing+With+the+Stars/Episode+104/episode/431956/summary.html | accessdate = 2009-05-06}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:95%; white-space:nowrap\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%\"|Couple\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Scores\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Dance\n! style=\"width:44%\"|Music\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Result\n|-\n| Joey & Erin\n| 20 (7, 6, 7)\n| Samba\n| \"[[Tequila (Champs song)|Tequila]]\"\u2014[[The Champs]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| Rachel & Ian\n| 25 (7, 9, 9) \n| Samba\n| \"[[Soul Bossa Nova]]\"\u2014[[Quincy Jones]]\n| Eliminated\n|-\n| John & Nicole\n| 21 (7, 8, 6)\n| Samba\n| \"[[Just the Two of Us (Grover Washington, Jr. song)|Just The Two of Us]]\"\u2014[[Grover Washington, Jr.]] and [[Bill Withers]]\n|Bottom two\n|-\n| Kelly & Brendan\n| 26 (9, 9, 8)\n| Samba\n| \"[[Bailamos]]\"\u2014[[Enrique Iglesias]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| John & Nicole<br />Rachel & Ian<br />Kelly & Brendan<br />Joey & Erin\n| N/A \n| Viennese waltz \n| colspan=2|\"[[I Got You Babe]]\"\u2014[[Sonny 