ton]]\n|-\n| John & Charl\u00f8tte\n| 20 (7, 7, 6)\n| Cha-cha-cha\n| \"[[September (Earth, Wind & Fire song)|September]]\"\u2014[[Earth, Wind & Fire]]\n|-\n| Trista & Louis\n| 18 (6, 6, 6)\n| Waltz\n| \"[[Come Away with Me]]\"\u2014[[Norah Jones]]\n|}\n\n===Week 2===\n;Running order<ref>{{cite web | title = Dancing with the Stars: Episode 102 | publisher = TV.com | url = http://www.tv.com/Dancing+With+the+Stars/Episode+102/episode/425537/summary.html | accessdate = 2009-05-06}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:95%; white-space:nowrap\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%\"|Couple\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Scores\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Dance\n! style=\"width:44%\"|Music\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Result\n|-\n| Rachel & Jonathan\n| 24 (8, 8, 8)\n| Rumba\n| \"[[I Don't Wanna Miss a Thing]]\"\u2014[[Aerosmith]] from ''[[Armageddon (1998 film)|Armageddon]]''\n| Bottom two\n|-\n| Joey & Ashly\n| 21 (8, 7, 6)\n| Quickstep\n| \"[[You're The One That I Want]]\"\u2014[[John Travolta]] and [[Olivia Newton-John]]\n|Safe\n|-\n| Trista & Louis\n| 19 (6, 7, 6)\n| Rumba\n| \"[[Endless Love (song)|Endless Love]]\"\u2014[[Diana Ross]] and [[Lionel Richie]]\n| Eliminated\n|-\n| John & Charl\u00f8tte\n| 26 (8, 9, 9)\n| Quickstep\n| \"[[Let's Face the Music and Dance]]\"\u2014[[Irving Berlin]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| Kelly & Alec\n| 17 (5, 6, 6)\n| Rumba\n| \"[[Hero (Enrique Iglesias song)|Hero]]\"\u2014[[Enrique Iglesias]]\n| Safe\n|-\n| Evander & Edyta\n| 14 (5, 4, 5)\n| Quickstep\n| \"[[It Don't Mean a Thing]]\"\u2014[[Duke Ellington]]\n| Safe\n|}\n\n===Week 3===\n;Running order<ref>{{cite web | title = Dancing with the Stars: Episode 103 | publisher = TV.com | url = http://www.tv.com/Dancing+With+the+Stars/Episode+103/episode/427769/summary.html | accessdate = 2009-05-06}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:95%; white-space:nowrap\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%\"|Couple\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Scores\n! style=\"width:12%\"|Dance\n! style=\"width:44%\"|Music\n! style=\"width:12